-competes govern where someone works. IP assignment, trade secret law, and non-solicitation govern what they do with what belongs to you.\\\")\\n- **3 FAQs** — unique operational anxieties, no repeated math from body\\n- **Bottom Line H2** — wraps without restating the article\\n- **2 H3s per H2**, each with 2 paragraphs of 4-6 sentences\\n- **Bridge protocol** on non-first paragraphs\\n- **H2 intro paragraphs** before first H3 in each section\\n- **SEO**: primary keyword in H1, first paragraph, H2, conclusion\\n- **No self-referencing**, no bold in body, no em-dashes, no contractions\\n- **Plain English founder voice** throughout\\n\\nFile is ready for Dawn's editorial review.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"api\": \"ollama\",\n          \"provider\": \"ollama\",\n          \"model\": \"minimax-m2.7:cloud\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 15906,\n            \"output\": 757,\n            \"totalTokens\": 16663,\n            \"cacheRead\": 0,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"timestamp\": 1775844454925,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"097e4f63\",\n            \"seq\": 4\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:subagent:c6427c1e-6994-4bb4-ba1f-e992517d1320\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-main-subagent-c6427c1e-6994-4bb4-ba1f-e992517d1320\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1775839972568,\n      \"sessionId\": \"172fd72d-8524-4ce7-9c70-977345d7d7b5\",\n      \"model\": \"minimax-m2.7:cloud\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 100000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 16163,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1775839861566,\n      \"endedAt\": 1775839972337,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 110191,\n     